Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located in the heart of Cairns CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Hotels are pleased to offer for sale the freehold going concern interest in the Ibis Styles Cairns. 

Key Investment Highlights:
- 75 room 3.5-star hotel featuring 24hr reception and lobby, tour desk, Castaways Restaurant & Bar, function room, meeting room, resort style swimming pool, manager’s residence and parking. 
- The hotel is currently owner operated under a franchise agreement with Accor Hotels, however offers vacant possession of this agreement.
- Freehold 2,506sqm site located in the heart of the Cairns CBD on the corner of Lake, Florence and Grafton Street. The hotel is directly opposite the new aquarium, new Cairns Performing Arts Centre (CPAC), Munro Martin Parklands and the Cairns 24 Hour Medical Centre and Day Surgery. 
- Set to benefit from the recovery of regional corporate travel, tourism and events.

- Address: 26-28 Bunting St, Bungalow Cairns  
- Land Area: 1084m2. No encumbrances
- Two x 2 level Queenslander buildings with a walkway driveway in-between
- Currently approved as a boarding house/backpackers for 12 rooms and 21 beds in various configurations
- Rooms are furnished with ceiling fans, PAYG air conditioning, linen, pillows, duvets, towels, side chest of drawers. Inventory available
- Private rooms have queen beds, fridges and their own TVs
- Two fully equipped kitchens
- In ground concrete pool, BBQ area, extensive gardens, veggie gardens, chicken coop
- Covered gazebo and yoga lawn area
- Currently easily managed by the owners with some casual staff as required
- Website: www.tropicdays.com.au

Tropic Days is best described as two impressive genuine 
Queenslander style accommodation houses, fully restored 
and converted into a relaxed popular and well recognised 
tourism asset just one kilometre outside of the Cairns CBD 
(20 min walk).

The property has been well maintained with all essential 
services and facilities in excellent condition. A welcoming, 
personal and friendly vibe is felt as soon as one enters the 
property and the online reviews consistently refer to the 
“home away from home” atmosphere. The current owners 
who have travelled extensively themselves have a “clean 
and comfortable” motto and priority as to how they have 
run this impressive asset which has been endorsed by the 
number of positive reviews on the various travel websites.
